sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Voice as Voice Processing
    participant LLM as LLM Planner
    participant Task as Task Decomposer
    participant Nav as Navigation
    participant Perception as Perception
    participant Manip as Manipulation
    participant Robot as Physical Robot

    User->>Voice: Speak command
    Voice->>LLM: Structured command
    LLM->>Task: Task plan
    Task->>Nav: Navigation task
    Task->>Perception: Perception task
    Task->>Manip: Manipulation task

    Nav->>Robot: Move to location
    Perception->>Robot: Sense environment
    Manip->>Robot: Manipulate object

    Robot->>Perception: Sensor feedback
    Robot->>Nav: Odometry feedback
    Robot->>Manip: Execution feedback

    Robot->>User: Task completion